I said I'm fine, my combat systems are fully operational, I don't 
need my eyes to see, I have my nose to guide me. Now stop arguing and 
find cover. better yet get back inside the Ark." Lunarpine shouted 
over the gunfire around him. "Prowl get her out of here."

(Don't bother replying, I'm leading to my next post.)
